      *         MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
      *                              TO COCV8611-NTOTALAMOUNT3-S
      *         MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
      *                              TO COCV8611-NTOTALAMOUNT3-MSG
      *         MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
