      *    END-IF.

      *--- Valores a positivo e negativo
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  (COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT3 < ZEROS
             AND  COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT3   > ZEROS)
             OR  (COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT3 > ZEROS
             AND  COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT3   < ZEROS)
