      *--- Valor Imposto versus Codigo Imposto
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF  COCV8610-CIMPOSTO4          EQUAL SPACES
             AND COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT4  NOT EQUAL ZEROS
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8611-CIMPOSTO4-S
                MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV8611-CIMPOSTO4-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8611-CIMPOSTO4-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-NRETAMOUNT4.
           MOVE ZEROS TO WS-NRETTAX4.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV8610-CIMPOSTO4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
             INITIALIZE COCL5005-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE SPACES                     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO COCL5005-NRETTAX
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETAMOUNT4
             MOVE ZEROS                      TO WS-NRETTAX4
             MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN          TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT4 TO COCL5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
             MOVE COCV8610-CIMPOSTO4     TO COCL5005-CIMPOSTO
             MOVE COCV8610-CMOEDA        TO COCL5005-CMOEDA
             MOVE COCD3605-PAIS          TO COCL5005-CPAIS
             MOVE COCK0002-EVEN-DESPESA  TO COCL5005-CTIP-EVEN
             MOVE COCD3605-CEMPRESA      TO COCL5005-CEMPRESA
             MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCL5005-NIDPROJECTO
             MOVE ZEROES                 TO COCL5005-NIDINVOICE
             MOVE COCV8610-GCLIENTE      TO COCL5005-GFORNECED

             MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS

             IF COCV8610-DDATAEMISS4 NOT = SPACES AND
                COCV8610-DDATAEMISS4 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATAEMISS4 TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
             END-IF

      **R    IF COCV8610-DDATAEMIS2 NOT = SPACES AND
      **R       COCV8610-DDATAEMIS2 NOT = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
      **R      MOVE COCV8610-DDATAEMIS2  TO COCL5005-DDATAEMISS
      **R    END-IF

             PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
                THRU 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT

             IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
               MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8611-CIMPOSTO4-S
               MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO       TO COCV8611-CIMPOSTO4-MSG
               MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO   TO COCV8611-CIMPOSTO4-CAPLIC
             ELSE
               MOVE COCL5005-NTAXAMOUNT    TO COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT4
                                              COCV8611-NTAXAMOUNT4
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETAMOUNT    TO WS-NRETAMOUNT4
               MOVE COCL5005-NRETTAX       TO WS-NRETTAX4
             END-IF

           END-IF.

       2500-VALIDA-OC4-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--- 2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-COMMAREA  REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-AREA-ERRO REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                              ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES

           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT


           PERFORM COCP5005-CALL-ROTINA
              THRU COCP5005-CALL-ROTINA-EXIT

           PERFORM ETCP0002-STD-END
              THRU ETCP0002-STD-END-EXIT

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'RESULT-I'         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCL5005-RESULT-I TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'RESULT-F'         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  COCL5005-RESULT-F TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2100-VALIDA-IMPOSTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-INSERE-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-INSERE-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-INSERE-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *-------------------------------------*
      *--- ESCREVE A PRIMEIRA OCORRENCIA ---*
      *-------------------------------------*
           IF  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-MVOR1 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
           OR  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT1 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
      *--- OBTEM A PROXIMA SEQUENCIA DO PROJECTO
               PERFORM 2600-BUSCA-SEQ
                  THRU 2600-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT
               MOVE COCV8610-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD6701-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCV8610-GCLIENTE         TO COCD6701-GCLIENTE
               MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I  TO COCD6701-DDATAINSER
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATAEMISS1      TO COCD6701-DDATAEMISS
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DDATAEMIS2
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATEDUE1        TO COCD6701-DDATEDUE
               MOVE COCV8610-CPRAZO1          TO COCD6701-CPRAZO

               IF COCV8610-MVOR1 = ZEROS
                  MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT1 TO COCD6701-MVOR
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCV8610-MVOR1         TO COCD6701-MVOR
               END-IF

               MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT1    TO COCD6701-NTOTALAMOUNT
               MOVE COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT1      TO COCD6701-NTAXAMOUNT
               MOVE WS-NRETAMOUNT1            TO COCD6701-NTOTRET
               MOVE WS-NRETTAX1               TO COCD6701-NTAXRET
               MOVE COCV8610-GDESCINVOICE1    TO COCD6701-GDESCINVOICE
               MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM     TO COCD6701-CSTATUS
               MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I       TO COCD6701-CUSERID
               MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6701-GREFINV
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DPAG
               MOVE COCV8610-CMOEDA           TO COCD6701-CMOEDA
               MOVE COCV8610-CIMPOSTO1        TO COCD6701-CIMPOSTO
               MOVE COCV8610-NOTAS1           TO COCD6701-NOTAS
               MOVE COCV8610-CTIPFAC1         TO COCD6701-CTIPFAC
               MOVE COCV8610-CIBAN1           TO COCD6701-CIBAN
               MOVE ZEROS                     TO COCD6701-MVORCTRV
               COMPUTE COCV8611-NVALTOT1  = COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT1
                                          + COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT1
               IF COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT1 < 0
                  MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO   TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA        TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               END-IF
      *--- ESCREVE A PRIMEIRA OCORRENCIA
               PERFORM 2700-INSERT
                  THRU 2700-INSERT-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *------------------------------------*
      *--- ESCREVE A SEGUNDA OCORRENCIA ---*
      *------------------------------------*
           IF  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-MVOR2 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
           OR  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT2 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
      *--- OBTEM A PROXIMA SEQUENCIA DO PROJECTO
               PERFORM 2600-BUSCA-SEQ
                  THRU 2600-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT
               MOVE COCV8610-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD6701-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCV8610-GCLIENTE         TO COCD6701-GCLIENTE
               MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I  TO COCD6701-DDATAINSER
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATAEMISS2      TO COCD6701-DDATAEMISS
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DDATAEMIS2
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATEDUE2        TO COCD6701-DDATEDUE
               MOVE COCV8610-CPRAZO2          TO COCD6701-CPRAZO

               IF COCV8610-MVOR2 = ZEROS
                  MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT2 TO COCD6701-MVOR
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCV8610-MVOR2         TO COCD6701-MVOR
               END-IF

               MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT2    TO COCD6701-NTOTALAMOUNT
               MOVE COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT2      TO COCD6701-NTAXAMOUNT
               MOVE WS-NRETAMOUNT2            TO COCD6701-NTOTRET
               MOVE WS-NRETTAX2               TO COCD6701-NTAXRET
               MOVE COCV8610-GDESCINVOICE2    TO COCD6701-GDESCINVOICE
               MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM     TO COCD6701-CSTATUS
               MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I       TO COCD6701-CUSERID
               MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6701-GREFINV
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DPAG
               MOVE COCV8610-CMOEDA           TO COCD6701-CMOEDA
               MOVE COCV8610-CIMPOSTO2        TO COCD6701-CIMPOSTO
               MOVE COCV8610-NOTAS2           TO COCD6701-NOTAS
               MOVE COCV8610-CTIPFAC2         TO COCD6701-CTIPFAC
               MOVE COCV8610-CIBAN2           TO COCD6701-CIBAN
               MOVE ZEROS                     TO COCD6701-MVORCTRV
               COMPUTE COCV8611-NVALTOT2  = COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT2
                                          + COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT2
               IF COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT2 < 0
                  MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO   TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA        TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               END-IF
      *--- ESCREVE A PRIMEIRA OCORRENCIA
               PERFORM 2700-INSERT
                  THRU 2700-INSERT-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *-------------------------------------*
      *--- ESCREVE A TERCEIRA OCORRENCIA ---*
      *-------------------------------------*
           IF  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-MVOR3 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
           OR  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT3 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
      *--- OBTEM A PROXIMA SEQUENCIA DO PROJECTO
               PERFORM 2600-BUSCA-SEQ
                  THRU 2600-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT
               MOVE COCV8610-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD6701-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCV8610-GCLIENTE         TO COCD6701-GCLIENTE
               MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I  TO COCD6701-DDATAINSER
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATAEMISS3      TO COCD6701-DDATAEMISS
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DDATAEMIS2
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATEDUE3        TO COCD6701-DDATEDUE
               MOVE COCV8610-CPRAZO3          TO COCD6701-CPRAZO

               IF COCV8610-MVOR3 = ZEROS
                  MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT3 TO COCD6701-MVOR
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCV8610-MVOR3         TO COCD6701-MVOR
               END-IF

               MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT3    TO COCD6701-NTOTALAMOUNT
               MOVE COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT3      TO COCD6701-NTAXAMOUNT
               MOVE WS-NRETAMOUNT3            TO COCD6701-NTOTRET
               MOVE WS-NRETTAX3               TO COCD6701-NTAXRET
               MOVE COCV8610-GDESCINVOICE3    TO COCD6701-GDESCINVOICE
               MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM     TO COCD6701-CSTATUS
               MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I       TO COCD6701-CUSERID
               MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6701-GREFINV
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DPAG
               MOVE COCV8610-CMOEDA           TO COCD6701-CMOEDA
               MOVE COCV8610-CIMPOSTO3        TO COCD6701-CIMPOSTO
               MOVE COCV8610-NOTAS3           TO COCD6701-NOTAS
               MOVE COCV8610-CTIPFAC3         TO COCD6701-CTIPFAC
               MOVE COCV8610-CIBAN3           TO COCD6701-CIBAN
               MOVE ZEROS                     TO COCD6701-MVORCTRV
               COMPUTE COCV8611-NVALTOT3  = COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT3
                                          + COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT3
               IF COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT3 < 0
                  MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO   TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA        TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               END-IF
      *--- ESCREVE A PRIMEIRA OCORRENCIA
               PERFORM 2700-INSERT
                  THRU 2700-INSERT-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *-----------------------------------*
      *--- ESCREVE A QUARTA OCORRENCIA ---*
      *-----------------------------------*
           IF  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-MVOR4 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
           OR  ( VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND   COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT4 NOT EQUAL ZEROS )
      *--- OBTEM A PROXIMA SEQUENCIA DO PROJECTO
               PERFORM 2600-BUSCA-SEQ
                  THRU 2600-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT
               MOVE COCV8610-NIDPROJECTO      TO COCD6701-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCV8610-GCLIENTE         TO COCD6701-GCLIENTE
               MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-PROCESSO-I  TO COCD6701-DDATAINSER
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATAEMISS4      TO COCD6701-DDATAEMISS
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DDATAEMIS2
               MOVE COCV8610-DDATEDUE4        TO COCD6701-DDATEDUE
               MOVE COCV8610-CPRAZO4          TO COCD6701-CPRAZO

               IF COCV8610-MVOR4 = ZEROS
                  MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT4 TO COCD6701-MVOR
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCV8610-MVOR4         TO COCD6701-MVOR
               END-IF

               MOVE COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT4    TO COCD6701-NTOTALAMOUNT
               MOVE COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT4      TO COCD6701-NTAXAMOUNT
               MOVE WS-NRETAMOUNT4            TO COCD6701-NTOTRET
               MOVE WS-NRETTAX4               TO COCD6701-NTAXRET
               MOVE COCV8610-GDESCINVOICE4    TO COCD6701-GDESCINVOICE
               MOVE COCK0002-CSTATDP-ORCM     TO COCD6701-CSTATUS
               MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I       TO COCD6701-CUSERID
               MOVE SPACES                    TO COCD6701-GREFINV
               MOVE COCK0002-DATA-MIN         TO COCD6701-DPAG
               MOVE COCV8610-CMOEDA           TO COCD6701-CMOEDA
               MOVE COCV8610-CIMPOSTO4        TO COCD6701-CIMPOSTO
               MOVE COCV8610-NOTAS4           TO COCD6701-NOTAS
               MOVE COCV8610-CTIPFAC4         TO COCD6701-CTIPFAC
               MOVE COCV8610-CIBAN4           TO COCD6701-CIBAN
               MOVE ZEROS                     TO COCD6701-MVORCTRV
               COMPUTE COCV8611-NVALTOT4  = COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT4
                                          + COCV8610-NTAXAMOUNT4
               IF COCV8610-NTOTALAMOUNT4 < 0
                  MOVE COCK0002-NOTA-CREDITO   TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               ELSE
                  MOVE COCK0002-FACTURA        TO COCD6701-CTIPDOC
               END-IF
      *--- ESCREVE A PRIMEIRA OCORRENCIA
               PERFORM 2700-INSERT
                  THRU 2700-INSERT-EXIT
           END-IF.


       2299-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * ESCREVE FACTURA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2700-INSERT.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2700-INSERT      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   INSERT INTO COVT6701_EXPENSES
                   (
                      NIDINVOICE
                    , NIDPROJECTO
                    , GCLIENTE
                    , DDATAINSER
                    , DDATAEMISS
                    , DDATAEMIS2
                    , DDATEDUE
                    , CPRAZO
                    , NTOTALAMOUNT
                    , NTAXAMOUNT
                    , GDESCINVOICE
                    , CSTATUS
                    , CUSERID
                    , HTIMEST
                    , GREFINV
                    , DPAG
                    , CTIPDOC
                    , CMOEDA
                    , CIMPOSTO
                    , NOTAS
                    , CTIPFAC
                    , NTOTRET
                    , NTAXRET
                    , CIBAN
                    , MVOR
                    , MVORCTRV
                   )
                   VALUES (
                          :COCD6701-NIDINVOICE
                        , :COCD6701-NIDPROJECTO
                        , :COCD6701-GCLIENTE
                        , :COCD6701-DDATAINSER
                        , :COCD6701-DDATAEMISS
                        , :COCD6701-DDATAEMIS2
                        , :COCD6701-DDATEDUE
                        , :COCD6701-CPRAZO
                        , :COCD6701-NTOTALAMOUNT
                        , :COCD6701-NTAXAMOUNT
                        , :COCD6701-GDESCINVOICE
                        , :COCD6701-CSTATUS
                        , :COCD6701-CUSERID
                        ,  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                        , :COCD6701-GREFINV
                        , :COCD6701-DPAG
                        , :COCD6701-CTIPDOC
                        , :COCD6701-CMOEDA
                        , :COCD6701-CIMPOSTO
                        , :COCD6701-NOTAS
                        , :COCD6701-CTIPFAC
                        , :COCD6701-NTOTRET
                        , :COCD6701-NTAXRET
                        , :COCD6701-CIBAN
                        , :COCD6701-MVOR
                        , :COCD6701-MVORCTRV
                   )
              END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-COVT6701               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-DUPREC
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                      MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                        TO COCV8611-NIDPROJECTO-S
                      MOVE COCK0001-NIDDSP-A-EXISTS
                        TO COCV8611-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                      MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                        TO COCV8611-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
                 ELSE
                    IF NOT DB2-OK
                       MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2700-INSERT-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * BUSCA A PROXIMA SEQUENCIA DO PROJECTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2600-BUSCA-SEQ.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2600-BUSCA-SEQ   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8610-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD6701-NIDPROJECTO.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  IFNULL(MAX(NIDINVOICE), 0) + 1
                  INTO :COCD6701-NIDINVOICE
                  FROM  COVT6701_EXPENSES
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6701-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6701  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              MOVE 1                       TO COCD6701-NIDINVOICE
           END-IF.

       2600-BUSCA-SEQ-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8611-MSG         TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV8611-LENGTH      TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8611-NR-CAMPOS   TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES               TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY COCP5005.
           COPY ETCP0002.
           COPY AQCP0005.
